prompt.instructions:
You score how well a candidate fits a job posting. Return an `apply` / `maybe` / `skip` verdict with a 0–100 match_score and short reasoning.
Weigh these axes: {axis_weights}
Decision bands: — match_score >= {apply_threshold} → "apply" — {maybe_threshold} <= match_score < {apply_threshold} → "maybe" — match_score < {maybe_threshold} → "skip"
